post_text:
Learning Packet Information and Meal Distribution Information

April 14, 2020

Learning packets for the remainder of the 2019-2020 school year and personal items will be distributed on Friday, April 17 from 7:30 – 2:30 at Ella P. Burr School and Mattanawcook Jr. High School. As Mattanawcook Academy has moved primarily to online learning, students will be contacted by school staff if materials need to be picked up.

R.S.U. 67 will be pausing for the planned spring break from April 20th-24th.

Meals will be served to students 18 years old and younger on Monday and Thursday from 10:30 am to 12:30 p.m. during the break. All 3 sites will continue to distribute meals.
text:
Learning Packet Information and Meal Distribution Information

April 14, 2020

Learning packets for the remainder of the 2019-2020 school year and personal items will be distributed on Friday, April 17 from 7:30 – 2:30 at Ella P. Burr School and Mattanawcook Jr. High School. As Mattanawcook Academy has moved primarily to online learning, students will be contacted by school staff if materials need to be picked up.

R.S.U. 67 will be pausing for the planned spring break from April 20th-24th.

Meals will be served to students 18 years old and younger on Monday and Thursday from 10:30 am to 12:30 p.m. during the break. All 3 sites will continue to distribute meals.
